#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_money_exchange
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_money_exchange`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_money_exchange` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `so_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_total_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `total_items` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `api` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `shop` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `address_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hash` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `manual_payment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'usd',
  `currency_rate_kh` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '1.0000',
  `currency_rate_bat` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '1.0000',
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `module_type` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'inventory',
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `image` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_qty` int(2) DEFAULT '1',
  `buy_term` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currencies` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sync_account` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `return_consignment` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `consignment_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `commission_amount` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_commission_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'due',
  `commission_note` text,
  `print_time` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`),
  KEY `biller_id` (`biller_id`),
  KEY `customer_id` (`customer_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_money_exchange_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_money_exchange_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_money_exchange_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `from_currency` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_currency` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `exchange_rate` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_unit_cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `original_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `commission` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`from_currency`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=14 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=13 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_multi_buys_prices
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_multi_buys_prices`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_multi_buys_prices` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `price_group_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `qty_from` decimal(5,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `qty_to` decimal(5,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `price_group_id` (`price_group_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_multi_transfer
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_multi_transfer`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_multi_transfer` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tran_no` tinyint(11) NOT NULL,
  `tran_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tran_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `account_code` int(19) DEFAULT '0',
  `amount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `narrative` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `description` varchar(250) DEFAULT '',
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `Account` (`account_code`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `TranDate` (`tran_date`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `tran_id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `reference_no` (`reference_no`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `created_by` (`created_by`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_notifications
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_notifications`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_notifications` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `comment` text NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `from_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `till_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `scope` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '3',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_options
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_options`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_options` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_order_ref
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_order_ref`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_order_ref` (
  `ref_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `bill_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bill_prefix` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_sale` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `so` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `st` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `stc` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `qu` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `po` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `pr` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `p` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `to` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pages`;

  `order_no` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,

  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,

  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT 'pending',

  `rate` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_benefits
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pay_benefits`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pay_benefits` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `month` tinyint(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `year` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_addition` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_deduction` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_cash_advanced` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_salaries_13
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pay_salaries_13`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pay_salaries_13` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `year` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `gross_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `annual_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nssf_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_salary_items

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pay_salary_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pay_salary_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `approved_att_id` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `salary_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `working_day` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `absent` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `permission` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `late` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `normal_ot` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `weekend_ot` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `holiday_ot` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `basic_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `absent_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `permission_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deduction` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `overtime` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `addition` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `additions` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `addition_amount` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `deductions` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deduction_amount` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `seniority` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `seniority_response_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `severance` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `indemnity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `severance_riel` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `indemnity_riel` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `nssf_salary_usd` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `nssf_salary_riel` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `contributory_nssf` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `pension_by_staff` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `pension_by_company` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `health_nssf` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `accident_nssf` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `gross_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `gross_salary_riel` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `spouse` tinyint(5) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `children` tinyint(5) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `spouse_children_reduction` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `Taxbasesalary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `pre_salary` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `cash_advanced` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_declaration` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_percent` float DEFAULT '0',
  `tax_payment` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_payment_riel` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_pay` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_paid` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `salary_paid` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `normal_ot_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `weekend_ot_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `holiday_ot_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_commission` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=186 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_salary_items_13

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `salary_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `annual_leave` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `al_rate` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `al_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_severance_items

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `severance_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `first_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `second_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `third_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `severance` char(20) NOT NULL,
  `total_usd` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_khr` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `usd_100` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `usd_50` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `usd_20` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `usd_10` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_20000` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_10000` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_5000` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_2000` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_1000` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_500` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `khr_100` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pay_severances
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pay_severances`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pay_severances` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `year` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `month` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `status` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_pay_severances` (`id`, `biller_id`, `date`, `year`, `month`, `position_id`, `department_id`, `group_id`, `total`, `note`, `status`, `attachment`, `paid_by`, `created_by`, `created_at`) VALUES (1, 3, '2023-05-19 23:37:00', '2023', '01', NULL, NULL, NULL, '5', NULL, 'pending', NULL, '1', 1, '2023-05-19 23:42:29');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_payment_term
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_payment_term`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_payment_term` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `description` varchar(55) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_day` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `due_day_for_discount` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `discount` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_payments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_payments`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_payments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reward_exchange_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `saving_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction_type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pawn_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `step_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_deposit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expense_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `transaction_id` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `cheque_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_cvv2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_holder` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_month` varchar(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_year` varchar(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_usd` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_khr` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_thb` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `penalty` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'income',
  `currency` varchar(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cheque_date` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cheque_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currencies` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos_paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `pos_balance` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `approval_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `discount_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_code` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `write_off` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid_amount` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency_rate` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `STL` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `commision_type` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `SA` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `transfer` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `transfer_amount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_charge` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `commission_product` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `commission_amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `payment_term` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_paid` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `penalty_paid` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `loan_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `fee_charge` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT '0.000',
  `installment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `installment_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `installment_customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `down_payment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  FULLTEXT KEY `paid_by` (`paid_by`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=47 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_payments_requested
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_payments_requested`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_payments_requested` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `purchase_return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `transaction_id` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `cheque_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_no` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_cvv2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_holder` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_month` varchar(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_year` varchar(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cc_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_usd` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_khr` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_thb` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cheque_date` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cheque_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currencies` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approval_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `discount_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `write_off` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid_amount` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency_rate` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_deposit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `bank_charge` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `payment_term` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_paid` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `penalty_paid` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `account_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  FULLTEXT KEY `paid_by` (`paid_by`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_paypal
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_paypal`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_paypal` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `active` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `account_email` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `paypal_currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USD',
  `fixed_charges` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2.00',
  `extra_charges_my` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '3.90',
  `extra_charges_other` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '4.40',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pos_register
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pos_register`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pos_register` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `cash_in_hand` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `total_cash` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cheques` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cc_slips` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cash_submitted` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cheques_submitted` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cc_slips_submitted` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `closed_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_opened_bills` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `closed_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pushed` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_pos_register` (`id`, `date`, `user_id`, `cash_in_hand`, `status`, `total_cash`, `total_cheques`, `total_cc_slips`, `total_cash_submitted`, `total_cheques_submitted`, `total_cc_slips_submitted`, `note`, `closed_at`, `transfer_opened_bills`, `closed_by`, `pushed`) VALUES (1, '2023-12-28 10:16:04', 1, '0.0000', 'open', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_pos_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_pos_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_pos_settings` (
  `pos_id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `cat_limit` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `pro_limit` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_category` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `show_category` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '8',
  `show_qty` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `show_item` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `default_customer` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_biller` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `default_warehouse` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `display_time` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'yes',
  `cf_title1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_title2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_value1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf_value2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receipt_printer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `allow_total_cash_in_hand` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `cash_drawer_codes` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `focus_add_item` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_manual_product` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_selection` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `add_customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `toggle_category_slider` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `toggle_subcategory_slider` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cancel_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `print_items_list` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `finalize_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `today_sale` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `open_hold_bills` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `close_register` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `keyboard` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `pos_printers` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `java_applet` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `product_button_color` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'default',
  `tooltips` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `paypal_pro` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `stripe` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',

  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,

  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `max_serial` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `morning_no` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `afteroon_no` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `evening_no` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `night_no` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_products`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `item_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `batch_numer` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_unit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USD',
  `other_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `other_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `alert_quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT '20.00',
  `sent_alert` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `expiry_alert_days` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `image` varchar(255) DEFAULT 'no_image.png',
  `category_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `subcategory_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `max_serial` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `tax_rate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `track_quantity` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `details` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `barcode_symbology` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'code128',
  `file` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_details` text,
  `tax_method` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `type` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'standard',
  `module_type` varchar(55) DEFAULT 'inventory',
  `supplier1` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier1price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `promotion` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `promo_price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `end_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier1_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier2_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier3_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier4_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier5_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brand` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `featured` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `weight` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hsn_code` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `views` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `overselling` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `hide` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `second_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hide_pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `depreciation` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `stock_type` varchar(255) DEFAULT '1',
  `gender` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `booking` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `blocking` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '11',
  `asset_price` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_length` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_width` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_height` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `p_weight` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `model` int(6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_medicince` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `stregth` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `code` (`code`),
  KEY `category_id` (`category_id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`),
  KEY `id_2` (`id`),
  KEY `category_id_2` (`category_id`),
  KEY `unit` (`unit`),
  KEY `brand` (`brand`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=18 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_progress_note
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_progress_note`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_progress_note` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `effective_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `doctor_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_projects
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_projects`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_projects` (
  `project_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `clients_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `end_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `target` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `updated_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `status` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  PRIMARY KEY (`project_id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_projects` (`project_id`, `date`, `biller_id`, `user_id`, `clients_id`, `customer_id`, `warehouse_id`, `project_name`, `project_code`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `target`, `description`, `updated_date`, `status`) VALUES (1, '2022-10-12 11:00:00', 3, 1, 2, NULL, NULL, 'Project A', 'P001', '0001-11-30 00:00:00', '0001-11-30 00:00:00', '0.00', '', '2022-09-20 16:37:43', 'pending');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_projects_plan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_projects_plan`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_projects_plan` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `title` varchar(250) NOT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `order_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rejected_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_date` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_purchase_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_purchase_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `payment_term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deadline` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_qty` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_projects_plan_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_projects_plan_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_projects_plan_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_plan_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `quantity_used` decimal(11,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `qoh` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `description` text,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`project_plan_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `start_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `end_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `store_sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `si_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `base_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `status_change` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `change_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `addition_type` varchar(125) DEFAULT NULL,
  `convert_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cb_avg` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cb_qty` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cbm` double DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_order_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_order_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_order_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `qoh` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `supplier_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `create_order` varchar(2) DEFAULT '0',
  `create_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_po` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `pri_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_plan_items

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_plan_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_plan_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `qoh` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `description` text,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_request_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_request_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_request_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_part_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `qoh` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `description` text,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_purchase_request_items` (`id`, `purchase_id`, `transfer_id`, `product_id`, `product_code`, `product_name`, `option_id`, `serial_no`, `net_unit_cost`, `quantity`, `warehouse_id`, `item_tax`, `tax_rate_id`, `tax`, `discount`, `item_discount`, `expiry`, `subtotal`, `quantity_balance`, `date`, `status`, `unit_cost`, `real_unit_cost`, `quantity_received`, `supplier_part_no`, `purchase_item_id`, `product_unit_id`, `product_unit_code`, `unit_quantity`, `qoh`, `description`, `gst`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`) VALUES (2, 1, NULL, 1, 'P01', 'Computer', NULL, NULL, '100.0000', '2.0000', 7, '0.0000', NULL, '', '0', '0.0000', NULL, '200.0000', '2.0000', '2022-10-12', 'Pending', '100.0000', '100.0000', '2.0000', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Unit', '2.0000', 2, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_shipping_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_shipping_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_shipping_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receive_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_cost` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_percent` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchase_shippings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchase_shippings`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchase_shippings` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receive_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `f_cost` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchases
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchases`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchases` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `purchase_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_plan_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `order_ref` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `request_ref` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_purchase_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_purchase_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_asset` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_code` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `useful_life` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `residual_value` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expenses_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'due',
  `confirm_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `suspend_note` varchar(150) DEFAULT NULL,
  `adjust_paid` decimal(11,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_qty` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `receive_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=24 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchases_order
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchases_order`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchases_order` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_ref` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rejected_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `suspend_note` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no_tax` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `tax_status` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_type` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_type` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_status` varchar(15) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `request_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deadline` date NOT NULL,
  `eta` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `received` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_purchases_request
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_purchases_request`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_purchases_request` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `supplier_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `paid` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `order_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rejected_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_date` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_purchase_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_purchase_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deadline` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `required_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_quote_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_quote_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_quote_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `quote_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `quote_id` (`quote_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,

  `service` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_repair_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_repair_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_repair_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `repair_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `technician_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warranty` text,
  `problem_note` text,
  `problem_status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'repairing',
  `currency_code` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency_rate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `quote_id` (`repair_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#

  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `project_id` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` double NOT NULL,
  `brand_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `model_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `machine_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `imei_number` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `receive_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` double DEFAULT '0',
  `order_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` double DEFAULT '0',
  `product_tax` double DEFAULT '0',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_total` double NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_reservation
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_reservation`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_reservation` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `note_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `checkIn` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `checkIn_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `checkOut` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `checkOut_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `duration` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `from` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `destination` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `timeout` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_reservation` (`id`, `note_id`, `sale_id`, `checkIn`, `checkIn_by`, `checkOut`, `checkOut_by`, `duration`, `from`, `destination`, `timeout`) VALUES (1, 14, 28, '2024-04-11 11:32:00', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_return_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_return_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_return_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `return_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `return_id` (`return_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`return_id`),
  KEY `return_id_2` (`return_id`,`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  KEY `supplier_id` (`supplier_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `order_tax_id` (`order_tax_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `created_by` (`created_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `updated_by` (`updated_by`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_concrete_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_concrete_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_concrete_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `con_sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `truck_charge` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_charge` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_generate
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_generate`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_generate` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `reference` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `month` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zone` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_generate_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_generate_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_generate_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `generate_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `check_in` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_out` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `purchase_unit_cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `original_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `max_serial` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `addition_type` varchar(125) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warranty` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `free` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `weight` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_weight` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `piece` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `wpiece` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `width` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `height` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `square` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `raw_materials` text,
  `combo_product` text,
  `extract_product` text,
  `extract_cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `commission` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'start datetime membership for gym',
  `end_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'end datetime membership for gym',
  `period_type` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `category_name` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `making_status` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `foc` float NOT NULL,
  `from_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `destination_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `timeout_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `timeout_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date_booking_ticket` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `room_option` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_row_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `consignment_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_id`,`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=73 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_order_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_order_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_order_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_order_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_received` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `max_serial` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `foc` float NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `width` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `height` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `square` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `concrete_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `concrete_ids` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_order_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `product_id_2` (`product_id`,`sale_order_id`),
  KEY `sale_id_2` (`sale_order_id`,`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_sale_order_items` (`id`, `sale_order_id`, `product_id`, `product_code`, `product_name`, `product_type`, `option_id`, `real_unit_price`, `net_unit_price`, `unit_price`, `quantity`, `unit_quantity`, `quantity_received`, `product_unit_id`, `product_unit_code`, `warehouse_id`, `to_warehouse_id`, `item_tax`, `tax_rate_id`, `tax`, `discount`, `item_discount`, `subtotal`, `serial_no`, `max_serial`, `comment`, `foc`, `gst`, `cgst`, `sgst`, `igst`, `width`, `height`, `square`, `expiry`, `sale_item_id`, `concrete_qty`, `concrete_ids`) VALUES (1, 1, 1, 'P01', 'Computer', 'standard', 1, '150.0000', '150.0000', '150.0000', '2.0000', '2.0000', '0.0000', 1, 'Unit', 7, NULL, '0.0000', NULL, '', '0', '0.0000', '300.0000', '', '', '', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sale_targets
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sale_targets`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sale_targets` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `start_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `end_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `multi_zone` varchar(225) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sales
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sales`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sales` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `so_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `po_number` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_total_price` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `total_items` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `buy_status` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `api` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `shop` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `address_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reserve_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hash` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `manual_payment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date_in` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `date_out` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'usd',
  `currency_rate_kh` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '1.0000',
  `currency_rate_bat` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '1.0000',
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `delivery_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_type` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'inventory',
  `is_loan` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `image` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `member_card_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `number_customer` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `customer_qty` int(2) DEFAULT '1',
  `original_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `expired_paid` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `zone_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_award_points` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `buy_term` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currencies` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `declare_tax` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `sync_account` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `return_consignment` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `consignment_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `commission_amount` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_commission_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'due',
  `commission_note` text,
  `print_time` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `produce_status` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `from_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `destination_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `time_out_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `wait_number` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `store_sale` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `installment` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `academic_year` varchar(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `fee_type` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `child_no` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `skill_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `membership_code` int(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `study_info_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_sync` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `pushed` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `diagnosis_id` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `patience_type` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bed_id` tinyint(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `chipmong` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `ar_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_request` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `shipping_request_phone` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping_request_address` text,
  `shipping_request_note` text,
  `fuel_sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`),
  KEY `biller_id` (`biller_id`),
  KEY `customer_id` (`customer_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=34 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sales_edit_request
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sales_edit_request`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sales_edit_request` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_reference_no` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updated_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `noted` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `active` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sales_order
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sales_order`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sales_order` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `order_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `delivery_status` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_items` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rounding` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `api` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `shop` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `address_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reserve_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hash` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `manual_payment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_type` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'inventory',
  `weight` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `height` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `temperature` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency_rate_kh` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `image` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `store_sale` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `symptoms` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `symptoms_description` text,
  `patience_type` char(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `diagnosis_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bed_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `location_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sales_rank_commission
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sales_rank_commission`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sales_rank_commission` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(200) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `start_rank` decimal(11,2) NOT NULL,
  `end_rank` decimal(11,2) NOT NULL,
  `commission` decimal(11,2) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_saving_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_saving_products`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_saving_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `initial_amount_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `initial_amount_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `balance_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `balance_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `withdraw_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `withdraw_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `withdraw_fee_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `withdraw_fee_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_fee_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_fee_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_fee_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_fee_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `entry_fee_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `entry_fee_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_savings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_savings`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_savings` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saving_product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saving_officer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `initial_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `entry_fee` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_fee` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `withdraw_fee` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_fee` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `reason` text,
  `closed_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `closed_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_savings_cancel_transactions
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_savings_cancel_transactions`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_savings_cancel_transactions` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saving_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `comment` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_service_package
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_service_package`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_service_package` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `package_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `service_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `qty` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL,
  `description` text CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sessions
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sessions`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sessions` (
  `id` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `ip_address` varchar(45) NOT NULL,
  `timestamp` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `data` blob NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `ci_sessions_timestamp` (`timestamp`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
