#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_settings` (
  `setting_id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `logo` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `logo2` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `site_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `other_site_name` varchar(150) DEFAULT NULL,
  `language` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `default_warehouse` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `accounting_method` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `default_currency` varchar(5) NOT NULL,
  `default_tax_rate` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `rows_per_page` int(2) NOT NULL,
  `version` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1.0',
  `default_tax_rate2` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `dateformat` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sales_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sales_order_prefix` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `sales_tax_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `boms_method` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `quote_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_request_prefix` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_order_prefix` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `transfer_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,

  `expense_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,

  `ppayment_prefix` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'POP',
  `item_addition` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `theme` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `product_serial` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,

  `invoice_discount_formate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_discount` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `discount_method` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `tax1` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `tax2` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `overselling` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',

  `thousands_sep` varchar(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT ',',
  `invoice_view` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `skill_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subject_id` text,
  `description` text,
  `score_type` char(20) DEFAULT 'average',
  `status` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'active',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=17 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_solutions
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_solutions`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_solutions` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `ticket_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `solution` text,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `belong_to` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `student_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `created_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_student_faults
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_student_faults`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_student_faults` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `student_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `class_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `blacklist` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `created_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_student_fees_master
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_student_fees_master`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_student_fees_master` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `student_session_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `fee_session_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` float(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `discount` varchar(100) DEFAULT '0',
  `amount_discount` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `is_active` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'no',
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `payment_status` char(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `invoice_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `student_session_id` (`student_session_id`),
  KEY `fee_session_group_id` (`fee_session_group_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=26 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_student_monthly
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_student_monthly`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_student_monthly` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `exam_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `year` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `month` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `student_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `class_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `class_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rank` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `score` decimal(5,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `average` decimal(5,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `result` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `credit` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `final` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_sh_student_monthly` (`id`, `exam_id`, `academic_year`, `year`, `month`, `biller_id`, `biller_name`, `student_id`, `program_id`, `program_name`, `section_id`, `section_name`, `grade_id`, `grade_name`, `class_id`, `class_name`, `rank`, `score`, `average`, `result`, `credit`, `final`) VALUES (3, 5, '2022', '2022', '07', 3, 'SBC SOLUTIONS', 10, 1, 'Bachloar Degree', 2, 'Semester 1', 2, 'Year II', 14, 'MKT-M2', 1, '80.00', '80.00', 'ngood', NULL, 0);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_student_sectionly
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_student_sectionly`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_student_sectionly` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `exam_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `student_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `class_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `class_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_rank` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_average` decimal(5,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `rank` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `average` decimal(5,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `result` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `credit` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_student_statuses
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_student_statuses`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_student_statuses` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `s_academic_year` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `from_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `status_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `student_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `review_status` char(10) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `review_note` text,
  `review_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `review_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `review_attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `status` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `study_info_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_students
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_students`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_students` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `code` varchar(225) DEFAULT '0',
  `number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `firstname` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lastname` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `firstname_other` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lastname_other` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gender` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `second_phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` text,
  `city_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `district_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `commune_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `pob` text,
  `religion` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nationality` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `family_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `child_no` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_child_no` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attached_application` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attached_test` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `skill_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `timeshift_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `photo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `previous_education` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `secondary_education` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `higher_education` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'active',
  `approval_status` char(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `is_admission` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `scholarship_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hs_degree_year` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `custom_field_1` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `custom_field_2` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `custom_field_3` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `custom_field_4` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `custom_field_5` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=49 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_study_infos
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_study_infos`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_study_infos` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `student_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `program` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `skill_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grade` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'semester',
  `class_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `class` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `batch` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `timeshift_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tuition_sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `issue_invoice` char(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `child_no` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `type` char(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(20) DEFAULT 'active',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `scholarship_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `generation` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `student_id` (`student_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `biller_id` (`biller_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `program_id` (`program_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `grade_id` (`grade_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `academic_year` (`academic_year`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=22 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_subjects
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_subjects`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_subjects` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `skill_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `status` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'active',
  `type` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'school',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=168 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_table_times
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_table_times`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_table_times` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `class_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `academic_year` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `section_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subject_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `teacher_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `room_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `day` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `end_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_sh_teacher_working_info
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_sh_teacher_working_info`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_sh_teacher_working_info` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `policy_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `resigned_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `self_tax` bigint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `salary_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `absent_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `permission_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_early_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `normal_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `holiday_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `weekend_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `kpi_type` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `additions` text,
  `deductions` text,
  `annual_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `special_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `sick_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `other_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `employee_id` (`employee_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `policy_id` (`policy_id`) USING BTREE

  `leave_deduction` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `overtime` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `loan` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `commission` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT '0.000',
  `net_salary` float(10,2) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `month` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `year` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `payment_mode` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `payment_date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `remark` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_step_payment
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_step_payment`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_step_payment` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` tinyint(11) NOT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(155) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pay_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_payment` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `balance` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(25) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `paid` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `register_date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `warehouse_id` int(5) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_count_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_count_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_count_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `stock_count_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `date_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_variant` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_variant_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expected` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `counted` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `stock_count_id` (`stock_count_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_counts
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_counts`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_counts` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `type` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `initial_file` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `final_file` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brands` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brand_names` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `categories` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `category_names` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `products` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rows` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `differences` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `matches` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `missing` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `finalized` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_movement
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_movement`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_movement` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transaction_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` double DEFAULT '0',
  `quantity` double DEFAULT '0',
  `unit_quantity` double DEFAULT '1',
  `unit_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `actual_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `option_id` (`option_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `date` (`date`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=119 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_received
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_received`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_received` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reward_exchange_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `re_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pu_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `si_reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dn_reference` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `truck` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=17 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_received_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_received_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_received_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `stock_received_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reward_exchange_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_cost` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` double NOT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` text,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cbm` double DEFAULT '0',
  `sup_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `quote_id` (`stock_received_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=49 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_stock_type
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_stock_type`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_stock_type` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `description` text CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_stock_type` (`id`, `name`, `description`) VALUES (1, 'Bar', 'Bar');
INSERT INTO `bpas_stock_type` (`id`, `name`, `description`) VALUES (2, 'Food', 'Food');
INSERT INTO `bpas_stock_type` (`id`, `name`, `description`) VALUES (3, 'Medicines', 'Medicines');
INSERT INTO `bpas_stock_type` (`id`, `name`, `description`) VALUES (7, 'Inventory', 'Inventory');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_suspended_addon_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_suspended_addon_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_suspended_addon_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `suspend_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(225) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `tax_rate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `addon_row_id` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `item_row_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `sale_item_id` (`suspend_item_id`),
  KEY `sale_id` (`suspend_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_suspended_assign
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_suspended_assign`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_suspended_assign` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `assign_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `patient_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bed` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `price` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` float DEFAULT '0',
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_suspended_bills
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_suspended_bills`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_suspended_bills` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `refer` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `start_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `count` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `table_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `table_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `print_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `bill_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `cgst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `original_price` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `free` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `suspend_note` (`suspend_note`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_suspended_items

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_suspended_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_suspended_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `item_row_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subcomment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount_description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,

  `sgst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,

  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `row_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_suspended_note`;

  `note_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `check_out` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `duration` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,

  `floor` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,

  `tmp` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`note_id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=15 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `user_id` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'new',
  `progress` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_transfer_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_transfer_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_transfer_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `transfer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `gst` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `transfer_id` (`transfer_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_transfers
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_transfers`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_transfers` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `transfer_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `from_biller` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_biller` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `from_warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `from_warehouse_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `from_warehouse_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `to_warehouse_name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_tax` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grand_total` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `accepted_by` tinyint(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shipping` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_user_audit_trails
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_user_audit_trails`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_user_audit_trails` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `event` enum('insert','update','delete') NOT NULL,
  `table_name` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `old_values` text,
  `new_values` text,
  `url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(128) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ip_address` varchar(45) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_agent` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2449 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_user_logins
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_user_logins`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_user_logins` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `company_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ip_address` varbinary(16) NOT NULL,
  `login` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `time` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=265 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_users
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_users`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_users` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `group_id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `emp_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `emp_code` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `first_name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `last_name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `username` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `gender` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `company` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(10) unsigned DEFAULT '1',
  `multi_biller` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `company_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `show_cost` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `show_price` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `view_right` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `edit_right` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `allow_discount` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `language` char(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'english',
  `active` tinyint(1) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `last_login` int(11) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `last_ip_address` varbinary(45) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ip_address` varbinary(45) NOT NULL,
  `pin_code` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `salt` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `activation_code` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `forgotten_password_code` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `forgotten_password_time` int(11) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `remember_code` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_on` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `avatar` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nationality` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `employeed_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `award_points` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `expired_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `zone_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `multi_zone` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `save_point` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `is_remote_allow` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '0=false, 1 =true',
  `basic_salary` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL,
  `commission` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL,
  `commission_product` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `saleman_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_group` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_commission` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `salesman_area` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `share_commissions` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payroll_option` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `signature` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `technician` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `password_reset_code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_commission_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `fuel_time_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `money_change` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `group_id` (`group_id`,`warehouse_id`,`biller_id`),
  KEY `group_id_2` (`group_id`,`company_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_users_bank_account
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_users_bank_account`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_users_bank_account` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bankaccount_code` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `user_id` (`user_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `bankaccount_code` (`bankaccount_code`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_variants
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_variants`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_variants` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_vehicles
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_vehicles`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_vehicles` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `model` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `driver_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  `fuel_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_voice_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_voice_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_voice_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_row_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_warehouses
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_warehouses`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_warehouses` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `address` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `map` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `atten_name` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `fax` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `logo` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_currency` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `overselling` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_warehouses_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_warehouses_products`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_warehouses_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `rack` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rack_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `avg_cost` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `qty_alert` decimal(15,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=35 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_warehouses_products_variants
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_warehouses_products_variants`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_warehouses_products_variants` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `option_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `rack` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `option_id` (`option_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_warehouses_products_variants` (`id`, `option_id`, `product_id`, `warehouse_id`, `quantity`, `rack`) VALUES (1, 1, 1, 7, '4.00', NULL);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_wishlist
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_wishlist`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_wishlist` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_zones
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_zones`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_zones` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `zone_code` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zone_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `city_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `district_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `commune_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `group_area_code` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;
